{"tid":547213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大撤銷劉子頎陳樂行停學令","createTime":"2018-02-01T08:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T09:47:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d161537d61660ab329af64bb2cbf295040525acf","tid":547213,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"浸會大學「佔領」語文中心風波有新發展，浸大撤銷學生會會長劉子頎及中醫學系學生陳樂行的停學令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1129136/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1129136%2F&d=6skEbpnF%2FXtZDxY%2F7yju5J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=758a7e3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1129136%2F&h=451f73c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1129136/</a>"},{"pid":"f912d7fb4473432f756e2c67fcf4679f8bf3563d","tid":547213,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"浸大鬧出不滿普通話豁免試評分機制的「佔領」事件後，浸大校長錢大康宣布，將劉子頎及陳樂行暫時停學。但隨著兩人早前親自到語文中心向相關教職員道歉後，錢大康對兩人的致歉舉動感欣慰，指校方會重新審視兩名學生的暫時停學令。"},{"pid":"d07e79d62b96d064503f0e7fe171efa4e66bbda8","tid":547213,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e295763517edc9f44a227a09c0343bfaf5464add","tid":547213,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19d7153a3c8f7ee9a42ebcd9b84fac584a28054","tid":547213,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"咁係咪可以收回道歉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmo